&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wakam.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wakam&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is a &lt;strong&gt;B2B2C digital insurer&lt;/strong&gt;, creating &lt;strong&gt;white-label and embedded insurance solutions&lt;/strong&gt; for 80+ partners across Europe. With operations in &lt;strong&gt;32 countries&lt;/strong&gt;, we are pioneering a transparent, tech-driven and mission-led approach to insurance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re transforming not only the insurance experience for our partners and their customers, but also the way we work internally. We foster a culture of &lt;strong&gt;autonomy, ownership, and impact&lt;/strong&gt;, supported by modern tools, AI, and data. Our People and Finance teams work hand in hand to create an environment where everyone can &lt;strong&gt;thrive, grow, and experiment&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🚀 About the Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll join our &lt;strong&gt;FP&amp;amp;A France team&lt;/strong&gt;, at the heart of strategic decision-making. The team’s mission is to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;clear, forward-looking financial insights&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to Executive Management and operational leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;robust, consistent financial steering&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;across multiple entities and geographies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;continuous improvement&lt;/strong&gt;, automation, and professionalization of our controlling and planning processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our new &lt;strong&gt;Senior&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;notion-enable-hover&quot; data-token-index=&quot;0&quot;&gt;FP&amp;amp;A Reporting, Forecasting &amp;amp; Transformation&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;you will report directly to the Head of FP&amp;amp;A and work closely with Accounting, Cash, Group Finance, and business leaders. This is a highly visible role with exposure to C‑level stakeholders and cross-functional projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🎯 Your Mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your mission is to provide &lt;strong&gt;reliable, insightful, and actionable financial steering&lt;/strong&gt; across Wakam&#39;s French perimeter, while contributing to the &lt;strong&gt;transformation of the FP&amp;amp;A function&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a key contributor to monthly reporting, quarterly closings, budgets, and forecasts, with a particular focus on&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;multi-entity consolidation, Balance Sheet and Cash forecasting&lt;/strong&gt;, and the &lt;strong&gt;professionalization of our tools and processes,&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;including acting as &lt;strong&gt;Product Owner of Pigment&lt;/strong&gt; for the entire Wakam scope.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multi-Entity Consolidation, Balance Sheet &amp;amp; Cash Forecasting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Centralize, review, and consolidate financial data from various stakeholders for the French entities (P&amp;amp;L, Balance Sheet, Cash Flow Plan &amp;amp; operational KPIs).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce &lt;strong&gt;consolidated analyses&lt;/strong&gt; in coordination with the team and propose &lt;strong&gt;optimization levers&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain &lt;strong&gt;forward-looking Balance Sheet projections&lt;/strong&gt; across the French entities, modelling key drivers (technical reserves, receivables/payables, intragroup positions, equity movements) and ensuring consistency with P&amp;amp;L and operational assumptions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Steer &lt;strong&gt;multi-entity Cash Forecasts&lt;/strong&gt; (short and medium term) across the French perimeter, anticipating liquidity needs, intragroup flows, and funding requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run &lt;strong&gt;s

